branchCategory.name: SJ
branchCategory.description: <p>The SJ series is a compact and low profile cassette based 4 port solenoid valve and manifold. &nbsp;SJ2000 measures 7.5mm wide, while the SJ3000 is 10mm wide and they can be combined to one manifold. &nbsp;The Vacuum Release Valve with Restrictor is also available.</p>

branchItem.name: 2000 Series
branchItem.description: <p>SJ2000 series provides flow rate up to 0.08 Cv in a 7.5mm valve body.  It is available as a Plug-in connector type or Non Plug-in individual wiring type.</p>

branchItem.name: 3000 Series
branchItem.description: <p>SJ3000 series provides flow rate up to 0.12 Cv in a 10mm valve body.  It is available as a plug-in connector type or Non plug-in individual wiring type.</p>

branchItem.name: SJ3A6
branchItem.description: <p>Series SJ3A6 is a vacuum release valve equipped with a restrictor to enable flow rate adjustment of released air. This space saving series is 10mm wide, designed in a cassette type format and uses a card-edge type connector. The SJ3A6 valves are compatible with Serial Interface units for both CC-Link and DeviceNet<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10pt;">&trade;</span> protocols.</p>
